## Completed Work This Session

### Project: herald — All 6 phases (Tasks #551-556)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/herald

Cross-platform desktop notification library, drop-in replacement for node-notifier. Zero dependencies. TypeScript with ESM+CJS dual build. Uses OS-native CLI tools: osascript (macOS), PowerShell+BurntToast/WinRT (Windows), notify-send/D-Bus (Linux). FallbackChain for ordered strategy attempts. node-notifier-compatible default export (callback+EventEmitter). Promise-based named export. Platform-aware shell escaping (POSIX, PowerShell, JXA). README with migration guide and comparison table.

80 tests. CI green (Node 18, 20, 22).

